      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 997.2 Carrera S in concours condition. This 3.8L DFI flat-six powerhouse delivers a linear 385 hp, paired with a sought-after 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is verified by a clean DME overrev report and consistent compression across all cylinders. Featuring PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) and a factory limited-slip differential, the handling remains razor-sharp. The undercarriage is pristine, showing no signs of salt exposure or fluid seepage. Finished in original paint with zero cosmetic defects and no bolster wear, this is an investment-grade example for the discerning purist.",
